name: thike
title: Emcee: Thike | FlipTop Battle League
description: FlipTop decided to give Thike a shot after watching his impressive 2009 freestyle battle against Damsa on YouTube. The Antipolo-based emcee faced the same opponent in his debut in the league and won by unanimous decision. Fast forward to the present, Thike continues to impress everyone with his hard-hitting punchlines and flawless delivery.
